	(text_box "PSU Phono pre-amp MM ECC88-ECC808 V2\n\nCustom Toroidal Transformer\nTotal Power : 36.00VA Frequency : 50Hz\nPrimaires: 1 x 0 - 230 V \nSecondaires: 1 x 0 - 200 V / 0.1 A (20.00 VA), 1 x 0 - 8 V / 2 A (16.00 VA)\nSupport SF01 + Electrostatic Screen + Magnetic Screen\n8V   : green=N, gray=L\n200V : mauve=N, white=L\n\nHV Power Supply LT3080 Maida v4\n6.3V@1.5A\n@230V => VOUT=6.37V, VC14=8.61V, VAC=95uVRMS\n@220V => VOUT=6.37V, VC14=8.08V\n\n6.3V@2A\n@230V => VOUT=6.35V, VC14=7.98V\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
